    Class Description
    BayCarMismatchExceptionTest
    Junit test for creation of BayCarMismatchException
    BayOccupiedExceptionTest
    Junit test for creation of BayOccupiedException

    Class to maintain service bays and interact with service manager.
    GarageTest

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BayCarMismatchException
    Class that extends Exception and is thrown if vehicle attempts to choose a service bay that is empty but of the wrong type for that vehicle.
    BayOccupiedException
    Class that extends Exception and is thrown when a vehicle attempts to choose a service bay that is occupied.
    NoAvailableBayException
    Exception to handle when a vehicle attempts to choose a service bay but all appropriate service bays are full.
